Paper: hep-th/9410022

Date: 1994-10-04

Title: Minimal Affinizations of Representations of Quantum Groups

caseAuthors: V. Chari

Comments: 19pages

We define the notion of a minimal affinization of an irreduciblerepresentation of $U_q(g)$. We prove that minimal affinizations exist andestablish their uniqueness in the rank 2 case.